
/*
 * The code snippet uses the [add] slot to append nodes retrieved by [get-nodes] from the [.arguments] node to the [where] node within a [data.read] node. This effectively combines argument nodes into the query's where clause, allowing for dynamic query criteria based on input arguments. 
 * 
 * 1. [add] - Appends nodes to the specified location.
 * 2. [get-nodes] - Retrieves nodes from the [.arguments] node.
 */
add:x:./*/data.read/*/where/*
   get-nodes:x:@.arguments/*
